name: Antique Style Handmade Arabian Wall Wood Shelf Console
description:
An antique style wall shelf. Made of solid wood. It is foldable. It has dark brown color.

The overall height is approx. 24". It is 41" width. The depth is about 10 1/2".

name: Antique Style Islamic Pierced Hand-Drilled Hand-Engraved Hanging Lantern
description:
This is an exquisite hand-drilled hand-engraved Lamp. It is BRAND NEW but made to look OLD. Made of brass and has a special oxidized-old paint. 

Specifications
Own Weight: 2 1/2 lbs
Height: 17"
Diameter: 8 1/4"

It comes with two marvelous double domes. You will be amazed with the fine engraving and perforation art of this lamp. 
It can hold up to 100 watt bulb. You can access the bulbs via the side hinged door. 
Measures approx. 24" tall with chains. With a ceiling ring. It is wired and ready to install.

name: Antique Style Jeweled beads/Glass Balls Boat Dual Chandelier
description:
This chandelier is made specially for this Listing, i.e. it is UNIQUE, you will never find alike any place allover the world. It is BRAND NEW but designed to look old. Made of brass and has a tarnished yellow finish. 

Specifications
Own Weight: 8 3/4 lbs
Width: 23"
Thick: 201/2"
Height: 14 3/4"

The body has a boat shape. Two beautiful lamp shades are coming out of the body. Both shades have curtains of beads hanged on its lower perimeter. The body is also decorated with many blue mouth-blown glass balls. The body and the shades are jeweled with multiple round glass colored stones. 
It comes with four hanging chains and a ceiling hook.
It can hold up to 2 X 100 watt bulbs.
It is ready for hard-wiring install.

name: Moroccan Style Colored Glass Pierced Pendant Lighting / Lantern
description:
This is a Unique Brand New lamp. It is made of brass and have an old yellow finish. It is finely etched and perforated. It is jeweled with multi-colored glass pieces. It comes with 3 hanging chains. 

Bulb is just hanging inside the lamp by the wire. Recommended bulb will be any standard 100 watt screw bulb. 

Measures approx.   19" tall with chains. Without chains measures 11". The maximum diameter of the body is about 8". It is ready for hard-wiring install.

name: Jeweled Moroccan Art Handmade Hanging Star Lamp / Lantern
description:
A very cool 3D Star Lamp. 12 pyramids attached together to form this lamp. Each pyramid has 5 faces and in each face a colored transparent round glass stone, that makes 60 colored stones (colors may be different than pictures). The top pyramid is hinged and furnished with a primeval sliding lock to access the bulb. 
Recommended bulb will be any standard 60 watt standard screw bulb. Looks beautiful when alight or not. It is made of brass. The perforated pyramids with the stones  will bring marvelous shadow on the adjacent walls. It has a gray antique finish. Measures approx. 15" tall with chains. The diameter of the star is 8". With a ceiling hook. Ready for hard-wiring.
